\nstyle=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">中国政府将今年的经济增长目标设在7.5%，尽管经济增速徘徊在政府目标附近的危险边缘，李克强依然重申不会出台新的刺激措施。<\/span><br\r\nstyle=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">李克强在周二召开的部分省区经济形势座谈会上表示，只要经济增长率、就业水平等不滑出“下限”，物价涨幅等不超出“上限”，政府就会着力调结构、促改革，推动经济转型升级。<\/span><br\r\nstyle=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\"><\/span><span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">李克强的表态说明，中国领导人承认，像过去那样通过不断加大对基建和房地产项目的信贷<\/span><i\r\nstyle=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">（请不要关闭窗口，本文内容稍后会有更新，并给你提醒）<\/i><span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">投放来刺激产出的方式是不可持续的。渣打集团(Standard\r\nChartered)中国经济学家李炜表示，新的促增长方式和以往不一样，他还称，中国领导人现在更看重能够带动经济长远发展的相关改革。<\/span><br style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif;\">此外，李克强的表态也暗示，中国政府对于经济放缓的容忍度要比外界想像的更高。汇丰(HSBC)中国经济学家马晓萍表示，以前觉得政府对GDP增速的底限是7%，现在看起来可能更低。<\/span><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"13-07-10 18:00","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2013-07-10 18:00:32","ShortDate":"07-10 18:00","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d188624359.u28925377.htm","UserID":28925377,"UserName":"ksam123456","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":593,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_595_0\">6月份保税区一日游金额占进出口总额7.09%，比5月份的6.89%还是上升的，出口加工厂真的不行了.江苏省6月份外贸额同比大概下降8%，昆山估计下降幅度更大，具体数字要到25日左右才公布.<\/di