an><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">8.9%<\/span><span>；上半年合并营收为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3209.69<\/span><span>亿元，较去年同期的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3358.04<\/span><span>亿元减少<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">4.42%<\/span><span>。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:18.75pt;\"><span>和硕<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">6<\/span><span>月合并营收<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">665.39<\/span><span>亿元，月减<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">7.65%<\/span><span>，年减<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">12.44%<\/span><span>；上半年合并营收<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">4253<\/span><span>亿元，年增<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">9.9%<\/span><span>。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:18.75pt;\"><span>英业达<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">6<\/span><span>月份合并营收为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">372.26<\/span><span>亿元，月增<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">4.74%<\/span><span>，年增<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3.97%<\/span><span>；上半年合并营收为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">2039.92<\/span><span>亿元，年成长率为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">0.46%<\/span><span>。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:18.75pt;\"><span>仁宝<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">6<\/span><span>月合并营收为<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">570.01<\/span><span>亿元，月增<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">7.5%<\/span><span>，但年减<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">9.3%<\/span><span>；上半年合并营收为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3343.7<\/span><span>亿元，年增<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">2.36%<\/span><span>。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:18.75pt;\"><span>广达<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">6<\/span><span>月合并营收<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">685.33<\/span><span>亿元，月增<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">12.2%<\/span><span>，年减<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">26.17%<\/span><span>；上半年合并营收为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3883.29<\/span><span>亿元，相较去年同期的<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">4737.43<\/span><span>亿元下滑<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">18%<\/span><span>。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:18.75pt;\"><span>展望后续，广达、和硕认为第<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\"> 3<\/span><span>季应有不错成长，看法相对乐观，英业达预估第<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\">3<\/span><span>季季增率有<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Simsun;\">10%<\/span><span>，仁宝及纬创则预估个位数成长。<\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Simsun;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"13-07-10 21:35","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2013-07-10 21:35:07","ShortDate":"07-10 21:35","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d188624359.u28925377.htm","UserID":28925377,"UserName":"ksam123456","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":598,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_600_0\"><div>\r\n<h1>拉迪：中国城镇化因果倒置<\/h1>\r\n<div>2013年07月10日 21:43 来源于 <a href=\"/t.asp?http://www.caixin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">财新网<\/a>\r\n| <a href=\"/t.asp?http://economy.caixin.com/2013-07-10/100554208.html#gocomment\" target=\"_self\">评论（<em>0<\/em>）<\/a><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<div>城镇化应当是经济增长的结果，而非驱动力<\/div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<dl>\r\n  <dt>　　<b>【财新网】（记者 倪伟峰）<\/b>彼得森国际经济研究所高级研究员尼古拉斯&#8226;拉迪（Nicholas Lardy）7月10日指出，中国的城镇化发展思路并不符合规律，政府的规划应当是如何增长和建立规则等。<\/dt>\r\n<\/dl>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>　　“我对城镇化感到怀疑，”拉迪在接受财新记者专访时说，“城镇化和发展的速度应当由需求来拉动，而非政府的规划，应当取决于经济的增长。”“城镇化不是经济发展的单一驱动力，应当是经济增长的结果，而非驱动力。”拉迪补充道。<\/p>\r\n<p>　　拉迪认为，目前中国政府在决策时，还是认为供给能够创造需求，“（政府认为），如果我们能把1亿人带到城市，那增长就会更快，但我不这么认为。”<\/p>\r\n<p>　　但拉迪也承认，中国城镇化的过程中会产生一些重要的制度性改革，比如户口改革等，但这仍然应当由市场来决定。“如果人们认为在城市里能够赚更多的钱，那就自行决定迁往城市；但若他们想留在原地，这也是他们的选择。”<\/p>\r\n<p>　　改革开放30年以来，中国的城镇化进程不断加快。截至2012年底，中国的城镇化率已达到52.57%，与世界平均水平大体相当。目前，中央政府正在制订国家城镇化规划。这一报告也将为中国未来的城镇化指引方向。<\/p>\r\n<p>　　但决策圈内，对于中国城镇化的路径还有纷争；同时，对城镇化担忧的声音也不断涌现。全国人大财经委副主任委员尹中卿6月29日在北京表示，从中国目前的城镇化规划来看，这是“一个半城镇化，是虚假的城镇化”。<\/p>\r\n<p>　　尹中卿认为，中国当前的户籍城镇化率远低于名义城镇化率。比如，未来预计有将近2.6亿农民进城务工，进入城镇居住，但是还没有成为真正的城市居民，享受不到城市的公共服务和社会保障。<\/p>\r\n<p>　　另外，土地城镇化率和人口城镇化率存在着严重的不平衡；中西部城镇化率远远低于东部城镇化率；小城市小城镇城镇化率远远落后于大城市、特大城市城镇化率等。尹中卿呼吁决策者摒弃传统城镇化思路，寻找新型城镇化道路。~<\/p>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"13-07-10 22:03","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2013-07-10 22:03:35","ShortDate":"07-10 22:03","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d188624359.u28925377.htm","UserID":28925377,"UserName":"ksam123456","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":599,"v_lPageCount":1.30000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}},{"docinfo":{}}],"DocRight":{"newdoc":[{"href":"206308529","title":"[活动回顾】2014.8.9大溪峡漂流记"},{"href":"206107553","title":"只为与你相遇，在你最美的时候――致.."},{"href":"206488366","title":"海上日出，曙光先照之回顾"},{"href":"206037064","title":"不忘人恩，不念